    <section aria-labelledby="fun-fact">
      <h2 id="fun-fact">Did You Know?</h2>
      <blockquote>
        The original Bolognese sauce, known as "ragù alla bolognese," is traditionally served with tagliatelle, not spaghetti!
      </blockquote>
